###Writing an equation

Our $\maroonD{\text{whole}}$ is the item's price $\maroonD{p}$, and the $\blueE{\text{part}}$ is how much money Marta pays $(\blueE{t})$ with the $\goldE{8}\%$ tax:

$\begin{align}
